quirement.", "create_time": "2026-04-08 16:15", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b5254a4b2c084e2c138342d278c3", "msg_type": "text", "sender": {"id": "ou_4dfe15a5bcafc6e258f66f1438175f63", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Zhuang Zhen", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "thread_id": "omt_1ab03377634f5982", "updated": false}, {"content": "can you help update the config and push to main? there are more than 200 partitions so it would take a while if run one by one", "create_time": "2026-04-08 16:24", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b525544c6c884e2e7c97f5934c52", "msg_type": "text", "sender": {"id": "ou_fc23e435ec45206118224d93a75e3995", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Rezha Julio Arly Pradana", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "thread_id": "omt_1ab03377634f5982", "updated": false}, {"content": "[Image: img_v3_0210i_adfe691b-6d69-427d-bf63-ccd33366eehu]\n Is this correct?", "create_time": "2026-04-08 16:30", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b52556c4e6884e1249529982b07d", "msg_type": "post", "sender": {"id": "ou_4dfe15a5bcafc6e258f66f1438175f63", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Zhuang Zhen", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "thread_id": "omt_1ab03377634f5982", "updated": true}, {"content": "@Rezha Julio Arly Pradana", "create_time": "2026-04-08 16:42", "deleted": false, "mentions": [{"id": "ou_fc23e435ec45206118224d93a75e3995", "key": "@_user_1", "name": "Rezha Julio Arly Pradana"}], "message_id": "om_x100b525500fd30a8e121585a8e1fe00", "msg_type": "text", "sender": {"id": "ou_4dfe15a5bcafc6e258f66f1438175f63", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Zhuang Zhen", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "thread_id": "omt_1ab03377634f5982", "updated": true}, {"content": "yes", "create_time": "2026-04-08 16:55", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b5255ce4ea4a0e2d3b22190e4de5", "msg_type": "text", "sender": {"id": "ou_fc23e435ec45206118224d93a75e3995", "id_type": "open_id